description: React component implementing family contacts management with state, rendering inputs, a table of contacts, and handlers for add, remove, and toggle primary contact.

methods.name: add
methods.description: Adds a new family contact to the state if the name is provided, then resets the draft state.

methods.name: remove
methods.description: Removes a contact identified by id from the state.

methods.name: togglePrimary
methods.description: Toggles the primary status of a contact by id.
